								<h3>SAML debugger</h3>
								<p>This tool is a webbased encoder and decoder of SAML messages. It is useful for debugging a SAML setup.</p>
								<p><a class="btn btn-mini" href="/samldebug">SAML debugger &raquo;</a></p>
							</div>
