								<h3>SAML-tracer<br /><small>Firefox plugin</small></h3>
								 <p>SAMLtrace is a Firefox plugin that allows you to trace and review all front-channel SAML messages sent as you browse web pages. The tool is intended for SAML developers or deployers for educational, research or debugging purposes.</p>
								<p><a class="btn btn-mini" href="https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/saml-tracer/">SAMLtracer &raquo;</a></p>
